yeah boring day. um it was really really stressful and i'd put full details but not that many people read this site or probably do just don't really care. so yeah leave comments sometime if you are reading this. make me feel special! well i have another poem. and after i wrote this poem during math it was then that i realized how much i despise that class. CAN SOMEBODY TELL ME? what do you do when the ones you love want you to chose? how do you handle it? how many tears do you need to cry? how many scars do you have to make? how many friends do you have to lose? and how many people do you hurt? because i have no clue how to handle it and i'm afraid to cry and i would run out of places for the scars and i don't want to lose anybody or watch them get hurt so hat do you do when the ones you love want you to chose? can somebody tell me? because i have no clue. yeah that's my beautiful poem! yup lovely. yeah i have nothing better to say now so i'm going to put some pretty pictures! this is a fucking awesome song!!! that'll be a while... tis true taking back sunday rox! luv this song

yeah this is my first live journal entry. yay me! okay yeah i have nothing better to put so i am going to put one of my poems. yeah i know...thrilling. the poem doesn't even have a name yet but hey i wrote it myself at 12 at night so gimmie a break. 

you say that i'm special
you say that i'm sweet 
but your words go right through me
houw can you say those nice things about me
when all of the world
seems to disagree?
you say that i'm pretty 
you say that i'm smart
but your words seem to have left me in the dark
how can you not just let me be
when all of the world 
is ignoring me?
you say that you love me 
you say that you'll stay
but your words are just that...words
how can you mea all those things you say
when all of the world
is so far away?

yes pretty i know. i am extrememly tired. they made my dosage not as strong for my medicine but it still makes me tired. oh and just wait till it wears off....hehe. and i have a dashboard confessional song stuck in my head. woah that doesn't happen often. well yeah i am going to go now. bye bye!
